  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc2.\u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 50 \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0b95\u0ba9\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "50 lakh vehicles registered for QR system",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Ministry of Power and Energy, 50 lakh vehicles have been registered for the national fuel card QR system introduced by the government for fuel distribution in the country.",
        "The Department of Information and Communication Technology has also requested the general public to register only through the official website launched by the government.",
        "QR The practice of distributing fuel by code has been implemented nationwide from today (01)."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "50",
          "label": "CARDINAL"
        }
      ],
